Package frc.robot.subsystems.shooter

Class ShooterPolicy

java.lang.Object
frc.robot.subsystems.shooter.ShooterPolicy
All Implemented Interfaces:
edu.wpi.first.util.sendable.Sendable, AutoCloseable
public class ShooterPolicy extends Object implements edu.wpi.first.util.sendable.Sendable, AutoCloseable
The Constants class provides a convenient place for teams to hold robot-wide numerical or boolean constants. This class should not be used for any other purpose. All constants should be declared

It is advised to statically import this class (or one of its inner classes) wherever the constants are needed, to reduce verbosity.
